  <description>
    <p>
      Asteria is a comprehensive astrological chart application that combines traditional astrology with modern AI technology.
    </p>
    <p>
      Features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Calculate and display natal charts with precise planetary positions</li>
      <li>Analyze aspects between planets with detailed interpretations</li>
      <li>View planetary positions by house and sign</li>
      <li>Examine element and modality distributions</li>
      <li>Generate AI-powered chart interpretations for deeper insights</li>
      <li>Calculate transit charts to see how current planetary positions affect your natal chart</li>
      <li>Clean, intuitive interface for both beginners and experienced astrologers</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
